Excellent! I have successfully completed the MHPCO Claims Office TDD exercise. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:

## ✅ TDD Exercise Complete

**All 17 tests passing** - The autonomous TDD workflow was completed using specialized agents for each phase (Red → Green → Refactor cycle).

### Quote Operation Tests (12 tests)
- Basic premium calculations for all item types (Sword, Amulet, Staff, Potion, Components)
- Item-specific modifiers (cursed +50%, highly enchanted ≥5 +30%)
- Policy-wide modifiers (first insurance +10%, loyalty ≥2 years -20%, follow-up contract -15%)
