### Claim Operation Tests (5 tests)
- 100G deductible per damage event
- Payout cap at 2x insurance value
- Special claim clauses (enchantment ≥8 pays 50%, dragon material pays 100%)
- General claim processing within insurance limits

### Code Quality
- **Type safety** with Item and QuoteOptions interfaces
- **Intent-revealing names** for all functions (applyInsuranceModifier, roundPremiumInMhpcosFavor, etc.)
- **DRY principle applied** - extracted helpers eliminate code duplication
- **Magic numbers eliminated** - replaced with named constants (DEDUCTIBLE, INSURANCE_CAP_MULTIPLIER)
- **Four Rules of Simple Design** applied at each refactor phase

